The paper discusses the use of deep convolutional neural nets and machine learning for building an agent that can play the game of Hex at a superhuman level. This falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), game theory (cs.GT), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE).
